---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Solid Foundation Increased Close Rate by 47% | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">8 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          How Solid Foundation Contracting Increased Close Rate by 47%
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          A Hamilton general contractor stopped losing leads to slow response and started winning more contracts with automation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
          <span>February 2026</span>
          <span class="mx-3">•</span>
          <span>Lead Flow North Team</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Results Banner -->
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Results at a Glance</h2>
            <p class="text-amber-100">After 8 months with Lead Flow North</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">47%</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Higher Close Rate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">3.2x</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">More Qualified Leads</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">127</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Google Reviews</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">68%</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Faster Response</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <!-- Client Overview -->
          <div class="bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Business:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Solid Foundation Contracting</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Hamilton, Ontario</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Type:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Residential renovation & custom builds</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Team Size:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Owner + 8 crew members</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Daniel Morrison started Solid Foundation Contracting in 2017 with a simple philosophy: do quality work at fair prices. His reputation grew through word of mouth, but so did his problems.
          </p>

          <p>
            "I was losing jobs to guys who weren't as good, just because they answered the phone faster," Daniel explains. "I'd be on a roof or in a client meeting, miss a call, and by the time I called back, they'd already signed with someone else."
          </p>

          <p>The numbers told the story:</p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>Average response time:</strong> 4-6 hours (sometimes next day)</li>
            <li><strong>Quote follow-up rate:</strong> Maybe 50% got one follow-up</li>
            <li><strong>Close rate:</strong> 23% of quotes</li>
            <li><strong>Google reviews:</strong> 23 (4.7 stars)</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented a complete lead and client communication system:</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Instant Lead Response</h3>

          <p>
            Every lead now gets an immediate automated response that thanks them, confirms receipt, and asks qualifying questions. Daniel reviews responses when he has time and follows up with qualified leads personally.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Automated Quote Follow-Up</h3>

          <p>
            After sending a proposal, automated follow-ups go out on days 1, 3, 7, 14, and 21. Each message is personalized to the project type and includes an easy way to respond.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. Review Request System</h3>

          <p>
            After every completed project, clients receive an automated review request at the perfect moment—right after the final walkthrough when satisfaction is highest.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <div class="overflow-x-auto my-8">
            <table class="min-w-full">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b-2 border-slate-300">
                  <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4">Metric</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">Before</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">After</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 pl-4">Change</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Response Time</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">4-6 hours</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Instant + 2hr personal</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">-68%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Close Rate</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">23%</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">34%</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">+47%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Google Reviews</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">23</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">127</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">+452%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Qualified Leads/Month</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">12</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">38</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">+217%</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "I'm closing 47% more jobs and I'm actually less stressed. The system handles the follow-up I always forgot to do. My reviews speak for themselves now—I don't have to sell as hard."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">— Daniel Morrison, Owner</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <!-- CTA Box -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Win More Contracts?</h3>
            <p class="text-amber-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see how we can implement similar results for your contracting business.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-amber-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
